description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Job Advert – Bank Facilities Assistant (Domestic and Catering)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Arnold Lodge, Cordelia Close LEICESTER&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for reliable and trustworthy individuals who can work in a demanding and busy hospital environment covering both domestic and catering duties who must be flexible, hardworking and energetic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Arnold Lodge is a Medium Secure Forensic Mental Health hospital. We provide care and treatment for individuals who have been admitted to us from other secure hospitals or from the prison service. Because of the specialised nature of the care, we are part of Nottinghamshire Healthcare NHS Trust although &lt;strong&gt;we are based in Leicester. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be part of the Facilities Services providing a cleaning and catering service to the wards and departments allowing flexibility to cover general cleaning duties aswell as assistance with the meal provision to the patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be able to deliver a high level of customer service whilst being able to meet compliance with food hygiene, high cleanliness standards and health and safety regulations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to work effectively and flexibly, both alone and as part of a team, maintaining a high standard of work will be essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have in-house training to help your personal development plans and will support you with all of your training.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The benefits include&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhanced rates for weekends and bank holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent pension&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-house training opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fantastic discounts for NHS staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please refer to the Job Description and Person Specification for more information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jacqui James - Facilities Coordinator Emai: jacqueline.james@nottshc.nhs.uk Phone: 0116 207 7806&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Or Leigh Greening/Sue Benstead on 0116 2077795 or 7761 to discuss&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
